the office of undergraduate education strives to help students explore academic programs, make informed decisions, and engage in a meaningful educational experience. they are committed to promoting and maintaining an engaging university experience for students from within and beyond the classroom. the office of undergraduate education oversees the development and operation of high quality academic programs to promote students' academic success. they play a critical role in academic advising and educational planning, degree auditing, and general education policy. action plan (2018) program plan (2017) program plan (2014) - not available. contact the team members directly or email us by area: accreditation@sjsu.edu academicassessment@sjsu.edu online@sjsu.edu programplanning@sjsu.edu  hours: mondays to fridays from 8:00 a.m. to 5:00 p.m. closed for most holidays and for lunch daily, 12:00 p.m. to 1:00 pm. 